=== PEA (Palmitoylethanolamide)

PEA activates PPAR-α, suppressing inflammatory gene transcription upstream of mediator release. Also stabilizes mast cells and modulates microglia. Meta-analysis of 11 RCTs (n=774) for pain @LangIlievich2023PEA. ==== If PEA works

mast cell or microglial inflammation was contributing. Mechanism distinct from LDN (TLR4) and antihistamines (receptor blockade) — suppresses at the nuclear receptor level.

*Certainty*   Low to Medium.

*Level of action*   Symptom management.